The source code was adapted for Linux by Klaas-Jan Stol.
These changes include: compiler warning fixes, update to 
modern C style (from K&R function declarations), removal 
of unused variables. The code was reformatted using the 
clang-format program, using the rules in the file 
".clang-format".

